', 'job_title': 'Graduate Software Engineer, Analytical Database (2026 Start)', 'employer_name': 'ByteDance', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRxzOQqTMRJYTyqM8PriHmQdOftNtg4IwVXp8qC&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.bytedance.com', 'job_publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/graduate-software-engineer-analytical-database-2026-start-singapore-bytedance-293-3320009/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/graduate-software-engineer-analytical-database-2026-start-singapore-bytedance-293-3320009/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://sg.expertini.com/job/graduate-software-engineer-analytical-database-2026-start-singapore-bytedance-293-3320009/', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Singapore Jobs Expertini'}], 'job_description': 'A global tech firm in Singapore is seeking a Software Engineer Graduate for a 2026 start. The role involves designing distributed database systems and requires a strong technical foundation, proficiency in programming languages like C, C++, Java, Python or Golang, and familiarity with distributed algorithms. Candidates should be recent graduates eager to explore AI technologies in database optimizations. Join a company that values creativity and innovation in tech, fostering an environment for meaningful growth.\\n#J-18808-Ljbffr', 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': '4 days ago', 'job_posted_at_timestamp': 1772150400, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': '2026-02-27T00:00:00.000Z', 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DjT99_U7LRFmrVCB6AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15113200', 'job_onet_job_zone': '4'}, {'job_id': 'UX1wIEeiu8FuK8QIAAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'AI Software Engineer |  Applied Machine Learning | ML', 'employer_name': 'Randstad', 'employer_logo': 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQnGi2f4uoxgnabfk515UOSB5L5BbLT5Hq0qaii&s=0', 'employer_website': 'https://www.randstadusa.com', 'job_publisher': 'Randstad', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://www.randstad.com/jobs/ai-software-engineer-%7C-applied-machine-learning-%7C-ml_singapore_46391002/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': False, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Randstad', 'apply_link': 'https://www.randstad.com/jobs/ai-software-engineer-%7C-applied-machine-learning-%7C-ml_singapore_46391002/?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'WhatJobs', 'apply_link': 'https://en-sg.whatjobs.com/jobs/algorithm-development?id=65969280&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://www.randstad.com/jobs/ai-software-engineer-%7C-applied-machine-learning-%7C-ml_singapore_46391002/', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Randstad'}], 'job_description': \"• Large scale AI project\\n• Strong support from business stakeholders to invest in AI\\n\\nAbout the company\\n\\nOur client is an established multi billion dollar company with over 30 years of experience who is a market leader within their industry. As part of their plan to invest in technology, they are now hiring an experienced AI Software Engineer to join their team\\n\\nAbout the job\\n\\nTaking AI/ML concepts from the drawing board to fully functional software applications\\n\\nLeverage the latest ML frameworks and AI models to write high-quality, scalable code that powers our products\\n\\nWork closely with business stakeholders, data engineers, and product managers to solve complex challenges and deliver solutions that create real business value\\n\\nProduce high-quality, well-tested code, adhering to the best practices and coding standards that drive excellence\\n\\nSkills and experience required\\n\\nAs a successful applicant, you will have hands-on experience deploying ML workloads on cloud platforms such as Microsoft Azure. Exposure to ML frameworks like PyTorch or Tensorflow will be of added advantage.\\n\\nProven track record in Python or data will be highly preferred.\\n\\nWhats on offer\\nThis is an excellent opportunity to join an established company with heavy investments in AI technology.\\n\\nTo apply online please use the 'apply' function, alternatively you can reach me at https://www.linkedin.com/in/hoonteck-nologyrecruitment. (EA: 94C3609/ R1219669)\\n\\nskills\\n\\nApplied Machine Learning, Microsoft Azure Machine Learning, Machine Learning Algorithms, Artificial Intelligence (AI),TensorFlow, python\\n\\nqualifications\\n\\nno additional qualifications required\\n\\neducation\\n\\nBachelor Degree\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DUX1wIEeiu8FuK8QIAAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': 'YEAR', 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '15111100', 'job_onet_job_zone': '5'}, {'job_id': 'S2JQVVKg2OaJOLt_AAAAAA==', 'job_title': 'Trading Systems Software Engineer', 'employer_name': 'BlockTech', 'employer_logo': None, 'employer_website': 'https://www.block-tech.io', 'job_publisher': 'Indeed', 'job_employment_type': 'Full-time', 'job_employment_types': ['FULLTIME'], 'job_apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=f42537b4b8c9b2b3&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'job_apply_is_direct': True, 'apply_options': [{'publisher': 'Indeed', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=f42537b4b8c9b2b3&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': True}, {'publisher': 'BeBee SG', 'apply_link': 'https://sg.bebee.com/job/65e54eae4d787c15962277c0166f37a1?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'publisher': 'Jaabz', 'apply_link': 'https://jaabz.com/jobs/154622-software-developer?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'is_direct': False}, {'apply_link': 'https://sg.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=f42537b4b8c9b2b3', 'is_direct': None, 'publisher': 'Indeed'}], 'job_description': \"Who are we looking for?\\n\\nBlockTech is a fast-paced algorithmic trading firm facilitating global cryptocurrency trading while expanding into regulated markets. As we continue to grow rapidly, we are looking for a Software Engineer to join us amid our exciting scale-up phase!\\n\\nWhat will you do?\\n• Design & build: Develop new ultra-low latency components in Rust, optimised for speed, scalability, and robustness.\\n• Optimise & scale: Enhance our existing trading infrastructure for maximum performance and reliability.\\n• Own your work: Drive projects from concept to deployment. Your code will directly influence trading performance.\\n• Collaborate across teams: Work closely with traders, quants, and fellow engineers to deliver state-of-the-art trading technology.\\n• Innovate: Experiment with new ideas. Creativity is encouraged and rewarded.\\n\\nWhat is in it for you?\\n• A permanent full-time position in a relaxed and trendy office located in the heart of Singapore's financial district (CBD)\\n• Competitive compensation consisting of a base salary combined with a very attractive bonus plan based on individual and company performance\\n• Outstanding performance is rewarded with the opportunity to buy into the trading fund\\n• Laptop, home office budget and transportation allowance\\n• Breakfast and warm lunch. Additionally, snacks and drinks are provided throughout the day.\\n• The opportunity to use state-of-the-art technology\\n• Extensive in-house training program in combination with an annual learning & development budget.\\n• Reimbursement of gym membership, sports events, the opportunity to do sports during working hours, and unlimited access to a psychologist.\\n• Regular social events, including bi-annual trips abroad, frequent outings, and weekly Friday drinks\\n• For internationals: All-in relocation package\\n\\nOur culture\\n\\nAt our core, we are a team of passionate trading and tech enthusiasts committed to revolutionizing trading through automation. Our collaborative approach ensures that everyone contributes to achieving our ambitious goals.\\n\\nIn this role, you will be both challenged and stretched, with ample opportunities for growth and development, both within and beyond your main responsibilities.\\n\\nWe invest in our people by offering competitive compensation and benefits, fostering innovation, and celebrating success. Our commitment to personal development transcends traditional norms; we provide an equal playing field, promote reverse leadership, and offer boundless growth opportunities for all our employees.\\n\\nJoin us to unlock your potential and drive innovation in the exciting world of algorithmic trading.\\n\\nEssential:\\n• 1+ years of experience as a Software Engineer, with a strong focus on systems-level optimisation and awareness of hardware constraints\\n• Expertise in Rust, C, and/or C++, with a willingness to work in Rust\\n• Deep understanding of TCP and UDP\\n• Experience with distributed systems\\n• A “finish what you start” mindset and high ownership\\n\\nBonus points for:\\n• Postgres and Linux Kernel knowledge\\n• Familiarity with Kafka/Redpanda internals, shared memory (SHM) protocols, or ultra-low latency system design\\n• Track record of building entirely new components from scratch.\\n\\nLocation: Singapore\\n\\nDepartment: Tech\\n\\nShort paragraph: As a Software Engineer at BlockTech, you’ll design and optimize ultra-low latency trading systems in Rust, shaping the performance of our global crypto operations. From concept to deployment, you’ll own impactful projects, collaborate with traders and quants, and innovate at the cutting edge of algorithmic trading technology.\", 'job_is_remote': False, 'job_posted_at': None, 'job_posted_at_timestamp': None, 'job_posted_at_datetime_utc': None, 'job_location': 'Singapore', 'job_city': None, 'job_state': None, 'job_country': 'SG', 'job_latitude': 1.352083, 'job_longitude': 103.819836, 'job_benefits': None, 'job_google_link': 'https://www.google.com/search?q=jobs&gl=us&hl=en&udm=8#vhid=vt%3D20/docid%3DS2JQVVKg2OaJOLt_AAAAAA%3D%3D&vssid=jobs-detail-viewer', 'job_salary': None, 'job_min_salary': None, 'job_max_salary': None, 'job_salary_period': None, 'job_highlights': {}, 'job_onet_soc': '41303100', 'job_onet_job_zone': '3'}]","logger":"airflow.task.operators.airflow.providers.standard.operators.python.PythonOperator","filename":"python.py","lineno":230}
